{"tid":2455714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄒家成獄中書信：8位被送中港人返港前夕","createTime":"2021-03-21T10:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T02:58:55.000Z","uid":126919,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a0dbf0c15c283a21ccee99b1471ddc5ebcbaf1d6","tid":2455714,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"【獄中書信：8位被送中港人返港前夕】 <br />\n <br />\n各位香港人： <br />\n <br />\n當你們看見這段文字時，應該就是其中8位被送中港人理應刑滿返港的日子（22日）的前夕。儘管可以預視，他們返港後必定會繼續受到沒完沒了的政治迫害，至少當刻，我仍與大家一樣暗暗期待著他們回來的一刻。 <br />\n <br />\n回想過去7個月，在向家屬和12人提供協助的過程中，情緒一直被事態的發展牽動著：時而擔心，時而憤怒，時而失望。但現時不論是整個社會的關注度，還是一眾日漸堅強的家屬，都令我不再憂心。 <br />\n <br />\n遺憾地，我無法與大家站在關口一同迎接8人返港，即使如此，我仍與各位同在。Save 12 HK Youths和Bring Them Back是我們的承諾，直至12港人悉數回港前，我們都必定不能忘記他們。12人當中，只要尚有一位港人未能返港，我們都與一眾家屬一直等下去。 <br />\n <br />\n鄒家成 <br />\n2020年3月17日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100206631386717/posts/486008549473188/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100206631386717%2Fposts%2F486008549473188%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=69753936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100206631386717/posts/486008549473188/</a>"},{"pid":"a8df5e9f1731351c2714b226e30fadddbf1d60bd","tid":2455714,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"d03ad8c9be33f59358bc598233053190b20cb533","tid":2455714,"uid":105691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2